{"tid":2228102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文VS習近平｜兩岸表彰抗疫英雄大不同 網民：一邊感恩一邊恩賜","createTime":"2020-10-03T09:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T02:10:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"98fb1896967f87fdf98e2ae7972617f4b7efe7e6","tid":2228102,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L6sOTi5U-MpjHkywstX6v4V28Xk=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QWJ443J5JBEAJKC2RZILXLS5RY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL6sOTi5U-MpjHkywstX6v4V28Xk%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQWJ443J5JBEAJKC2RZILXLS5RY.jpg&h=e65f8838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩岸表彰抗疫英雄的場面大不同，近日成為網民熱話。（互聯網）<br />\n...<br />\n兩岸文化差異有幾大，從近日在互聯網瘋傳的這兩張照片可見一班。同是表彰抗疫前線醫護及相關人員，在這邊廂的台灣，如同中學禮堂的台上，受表彰的醫護人員挺直腰、抬起頭，在台上邁着步，總統蔡英文逐一向他們致以深深的鞠躬，所展現的卻是「禮賢下士」、「民為貴，社稷次之，君為輕」的民本主義精神；而在那邊廂，「宏偉、瑰麗」的北京人民大會堂上，受勳者表現恭恭敬敬向中共總書記習近平90度鞠躬，雙眼還不能直視對方，生怕有所冒犯，完全呈現出那種「君與臣」、「主子與奴才」的傳統父權宗法主義文化。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/FX7V4QJR4BHCJLZ5BZVPTVB6QE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2FFX7V4QJR4BHCJLZ5BZVPTVB6QE%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=9064332e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201003%2FFX7V4QJR4BHCJLZ5BZVPTVB6QE%2F&h=e6091ad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201003/FX7V4QJR4BHCJLZ5BZVPTVB6QE/</a>"},{"pid":"2cf35c1ef378246312e1c8da5c99cacc710960c6","tid":2228102,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"香港啲豬肉獎冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73994f3983ad7c3d46193e6a3c34c47de36b2ee5","tid":2228102,"uid":264426,